---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Full Service Automation — Formic"
  description="Formic Full Service Automation provides manufacturers with robotic automation systems, fully managed service, and production intelligence software under one fixed monthly price. No capital expenditure required."
  ogTitle="Full Service Automation — Formic"
  ogDescription="Robotics, service, and production intelligence under one fixed monthly price. No CapEx. Performance SLAs included."
>
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://formic.co/full-service" slot="head" />
  <style is:global slot="head">
    .fs-yt-wrap{position:relative;width:100%;max-width:1080px;margin:0 auto;aspect-ratio:16/9;background:#000;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08)}
    .fs-yt-wrap iframe{position:absolute;inset:0;width:100%;height:100%;border:0}
    .fs-qgrid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(320px,1fr));gap:1px;background:var(--lgrey);border:1px solid var(--lgrey)}
    .fs-qcard{background:var(--white);padding:36px 34px;text-decoration:none;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:14px;color:inherit}
    .fs-qcard blockquote{font-family:var(--sans);font-size:18px;font-weight:300;line-height:1.5;color:var(--black);margin:0;letter-spacing:-.005em}
    .fs-qcard .fs-qattr{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey)}
    .fs-qcard .fs-qlink{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--orange);margin-top:auto}
  </style>

<div class="detail-bc">
  <a href="/">Home</a><span class="sep">/</span>Full Service Automation
</div>

<section class="detail-hero">
  <div class="si">
    <div class="slabel" style="color:var(--orange)">What is Full Service Automation?</div>
    <h1>Full Service Automation.<br><em>Everything. Included.</em></h1>
    <p class="lede">Formic Full Service Automation provides manufacturers with robotic automation systems, fully managed service, and production intelligence software under one fixed monthly price. No capital expenditure required. We scope your line, build the system, install it, and stay on it for life.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dark">
  <div class="detail-video wide">
    <div class="detail-video-frame">
      <video autoplay muted loop playsinline poster="/ECOS-Palletizing-Cell.jpg">
        <source src="/Formic-Header.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
      </video>
      <span class="dv-cap">Full Service Automation · what's included</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white">
  <div class="db-grid">
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">01 — How It Works</div>
      <h2>From inquiry to <em>running production</em> in weeks.</h2>
      <p>The traditional automation model takes 12–18 months and millions in CapEx to deploy a single line. Formic compresses that into weeks with no capital risk, and stays on the line forever.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>Free application scoping and engineering review on your line</li>
        <li>Pre-engineered system designs deployed in days, not months</li>
        <li>Installation and commissioning by Formic engineers — on-site, start to finish</li>
        <li>Performance monitoring and SLAs from day one</li>
        <li>Continuous OTA upgrades</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="/#cta" class="larr">Talk to an engineer →</a>
      <p style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:14px;font-weight:300;color:var(--dgrey);margin:20px 0 0;max-width:560px">Want a place to start? Read <a href="https://land.formic.co/automate-now-1" style="color:var(--orange);font-weight:500;text-decoration:none">Automate NOW</a> — the Formic guide to getting started with automation.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/Operator-Backview-Line.jpg" alt="Customer plant operator working a Formic-automated line — the team that benefits when Full Service handles the rest" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">Scope · Build · Run</span></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block lgrey">
  <div class="db-grid flip">
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/Formic-FPI-Dashboard.jpg" alt="Two plant operators in hairnets reviewing live Formic Production Intelligence dashboards — pallets per hour and run-rate broken down for the line" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">Cortex · Core · FPI</span></div>
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">02 — Software &amp; Technology</div>
      <h2>The intelligence behind <em>every system</em>.</h2>
      <p>Every Formic system is connected, monitored, and continuously improved by software built in-house. Real-time visibility, remote diagnostics, and OTA updates mean every customer benefits from every deployment.</p>
      <p>Formic Cortex handles fleet intelligence and operator UX. Formic Core delivers deterministic PLC control on industrial-grade hardware.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li><strong>Cortex</strong> — software intelligence layer for fleet management and operator UX</li>
        <li><strong>Core</strong> — deterministic PLC control on industrial-grade hardware</li>
        <li>Real-time OEE, throughput, and cycle-time analytics, accessible to your team</li>
        <li>Encrypted remote diagnostics — most issues resolved without a site visit</li>
        <li>Backward-compatible feature releases across every deployed system</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="/magic" class="larr">Inside the platform →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white">
  <div class="db-grid">
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">03 — Equipment &amp; Flex</div>
      <h2>Modular hardware that <em>flexes with your line</em>.</h2>
      <p>Standardized modular hardware means every Formic system shares the same building blocks. Easy to deploy, maintain, and swap as your line evolves.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>KUKA, ABB, FANUC, and Doosan robots — unified under one OS</li>
        <li>Swap or scale equipment without renegotiating your monthly agreement</li>
        <li>Backward-compatible upgrades across every deployment</li>
        <li>Field-tested designs deployed at scale — not custom one-offs</li>
        <li>Standardized spare-parts inventory across every site</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="/solutions" class="larr">See solutions →</a>
    </div>
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/Formic-Cobot-Pair.jpg" alt="Two Formic-branded cobot arms on a clean facility floor — modular, standardized hardware" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">Modular · Flexible · Standardized</span></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dgrey">
  <div class="db-grid flip">
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/Formic-Engineer-On-Robot.jpg" alt="Formic field service engineer working on a robotic cell — the included service that keeps every system running" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">24/7 · Bilingual · SLA-backed</span></div>
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">04 — Service &amp; Parts</div>
      <h2>Keeping the system <em>running</em>.</h2>
      <p>Service is the whole job. That's why it's included, not invoiced. Formic provides 24/7 bilingual technical support, regional Field Service Engineers, and fully managed spare-parts inventory for every deployed system.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>24/7 tech support — English and Spanish, every shift</li>
        <li>Regional Field Service Engineer network for rapid on-site response</li>
        <li>Performance SLAs written into every Full Service agreement</li>
        <li>Spare-parts inventory managed by Formic — no PO scrambles</li>
        <li>Predictive maintenance flagged before it becomes downtime</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="/#cta" class="larr">Get started →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dark">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:80px;text-align:center">
    <div class="db-tag" style="justify-content:center">Get started, the easy way</div>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:clamp(32px,4vw,56px);font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.02em;line-height:1.05;color:var(--white);margin:8px 0 28px">Success <em style="color:var(--orange);font-style:normal">from day one</em>.</h2>
    <div class="fs-yt-wrap">
      <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/SD0UMnNYR1E" title="Formic Full Service Automation" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen loading="lazy"></iframe>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white" style="padding:96px 80px">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:0">
    <div class="db-tag">Take the complexity out of automation</div>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:clamp(32px,4vw,56px);font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.02em;line-height:1.05;color:var(--black);margin:8px 0 32px">In their <em style="color:var(--orange);font-style:normal">own words</em>.</h2>
    <div class="fs-qgrid">
      <a class="fs-qcard" href="/stories/camerons-coffee">
        <blockquote>"Formic removes all the anxiety of a traditional equipment purchase. We like that they provide the entire solution, including committed uptime and service."</blockquote>
        <div class="fs-qattr">Cameron's Coffee</div>
        <span class="fs-qlink">Read the story →</span>
      </a>
      <a class="fs-qcard" href="/stories/uncle-crumbles">
        <blockquote>"With Formic, we were able to say 'Let's get it in here now' and start our automation plan quickly. If our customers want something different, we have the option to change and shift quickly."</blockquote>
        <div class="fs-qattr">Uncle Crumbles</div>
        <span class="fs-qlink">Read the story →</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-cta">
  <h2>No CapEx. No Risk.<br><em>No Problems.</em></h2>
  <div class="btn-row">
    <a href="/contact/get-a-quote" class="btn-ctadark">Get a Quote</a>
    <a href="/stories" class="btn-ctawh">Customer Stories</a>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
